title: Ep. 50 :: Why Stocks Are Pricing-In Strong Earnings
itunes:title: Why Stocks Are Pricing-In Strong Earnings
description: Braden Copeland, Co-Editor of the Stansberry Investment Advisory, talks about China's huge growth potential. Marc Lichtenfeld, Editor of the Activist Trader, tells us why following Carl Icahn and Daniel Loeb could make you a lot of money. Also, Frank breaks down earnings and answers your questions.
